These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Movie-Genre: adventure, horror, disaster, drama
Pet: dog, goat, horse, mouse
1. Pet:mouse is on the left of Movie-Genre:disaster##1
2. Movie-Genre:adventure is on the left of Pet:goat##1
3. Movie-Genre:drama is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:horse is on the left or right of Pet:mouse##3
5. Movie-Genre:adventure is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure | horror | drama | disaster |
| Pet        | dog | goat   | mouse | horse    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: crime, musical, scientific, superhero
Pet: turtle, fish, horse, dog
1. Movie-Genre:musical is on the left of Movie-Genre:superhero##1
2. Pet:turtle is on the left of Pet:horse##1
3. Pet:horse is in an odd position##4
4. Pet:turtle == Movie-Genre:crime##1
5. Pet:fish is on the right of Pet:horse##1
6. Pet:turtle == Movie-Genre:crime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | crime  | musical  | superhero |
| Pet   | dog    | turtle | horse | fish    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Food: carrot, grapes, pomegranate, watermelon
Hobby: magic-tricks, card-games, camping, fishing
1. Food:watermelon is on the left or right of Hobby:fishing##3
2. Food:pomegranate is in an even position##4
3. Hobby:fishing is on the left or right of Food:grapes##3
4. Hobby:fishing is on the right of Hobby:camping##1
5. Hobby:magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
6. Food:grapes is on the right of Food:pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | watermelon | pomegranate | grapes    | carrot      |
| Hobby   | camping        | fishing     | magic-tricks | card-games |

