.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
Hobby: cooking, drawing, reading, woodworking
Cigar: dannemann, davidoff, siglo, montecristo
1. Hobby:drawing is between Cigar:dannemann and Cigar:montecristo##2
2. Hobby:woodworking is on the left of Hobby:cooking##1
3. Cigar:siglo is in an odd position##4
4. Cigar:davidoff is on the left of Cigar:montecristo##1
5. Cigar:davidoff is on the right of Hobby:cooking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | cooking | drawing | reading |
| Cigar   | siglo       | dannemann   | davidoff    | montecristo  |

