.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Sport: skateboarding, handball, sailing, water-polo
Nationality: american, australian, indian, russian
1. Sport:sailing is on the right of Nationality:russian##1
2. Nationality:australian == Sport:water-polo##1
3. Nationality:indian is on the right of Sport:skateboarding##1
4. Sport:handball is on the far left##1
5. Sport:sailing is in an odd position##4
6. Nationality:american is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Sport   | handball  | skateboarding    | sailing   | water-polo       |
| Nationality   | american | russian | indian | australian |

