3. Sport:soccer is between Sport:cycling and Beverage:juice##2
4. Beverage:almond-milk is in an odd position##4
5. Sport:soccer is on the left or right of Sport:cycling##3
6. Beverage:cola is on the left or right of Sport:snowboarding##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola       | juice   | almond-milk | soy-milk |
| Sport   | volleyball | snowboarding | soccer        | cycling    |

